1. Moj *vrt* je prepun povrća. (My *garden* is full of vegetables.)
2. Želim da *vrtim* ovaj ključ u bravi. (I want to *turn* this key in the lock.)
3. *Vrt*ić je pun dece koja se igraju. (The *kindergarten* is full of children playing.)
4. Ona *vrta* pramen kose oko prsta. (She *twirls* a strand of hair around her finger.)
5. Moj deda je proveo svoj život *vrt*eći zemlju. (My grandfather spent his life *tilling* the soil.)
6. On je *vrt*eo glavom kad je čuo loše vesti. (He *shook* his head when he heard the bad news.)
7. Kuća ima veliki *vrt* oko sebe. (The house has a large *yard* around it.)
8. *Vrt*larstvo je veoma popularno u mom kraju. (Gardening is very popular in my area.)
9. Ona voli da gleda *vrt* koji se nalazi ispred kuće. (She likes to watch the *flower bed* in front of the house.)
10. Stavićeš ovu biljku u saksiju i držati je u *vrt*u. (You will put this plant in a pot and keep it in the *indoor garden*.)